}}

{{der-top|Compounds}}
* {{ja-r|映る|うつる}}: to be [[reflect|reflected]]; to [[appear]] as an [[image]]; to [[match]] or go well with something {{qualifier|in terms of color coordination}}
{{der-bottom}}

{{ja-kanjitab|えい|yomi=kanon}}
From {{der|ja|ltc|sort=えい|-}} {{ltc-l|映|id=2}}.

The ''[[漢音#Japanese|kan'on]]'' pronunciation, so likely a later borrowing.

{{der-top}}
* {{ja-r|映画|えいが}}: a [[movie]]
* {{ja-r|映写|えいしゃ}}: a [[projection]]; to [[project]] something {{qualifier|an image}}
* {{ja-r|映像|えいぞう}}: an [[image]] {{qualifier|especially one on a screen or in one's mind}}, a [[reflection]]
{{der-bottom}}
